0010 REM "WOE - Closed WO Entry (Lot/Serial Processing"
0020 REM "Program WOE.EB"
0022 REM "+-----------------------------------------------------------+"
0024 REM "| ADD+ON Software, Inc. Advantage/V Version 6.0.0 - 15May96 |"
